{"4542410": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Fundoshinobi: The Naked Ninja", "steam_appid": 4542410, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/58b8a33264f8a7a5853b1cfe697abee9.avif?t=1775176158\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Information</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you become &quot;Sho,&quot; the successor of a ninja clan that dons only the traditional <i>fundoshi</i> loincloth. Your mission is to purify women who have been tainted by dark Yin energy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/eeb794fd510f8ab1ff1b3d37896e54e4.avif?t=1775176158\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game progresses through various stages, each consisting of several sub-stages. You can equip up to 4 weapons and synthesize them up to level 4 for devastating power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/5eae7a157d82a487c0dfdce0750b8c71.avif?t=1775176158\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/7054bed9fa89dd1cb2a4bf3ccf5fcd5c.avif?t=1775176158\" width=640 height=360 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the time limit for a sub-stage expires, a boss with unique attack patterns will appear. Defeat them to begin the purification process. For a complete purification, Sho’s Yang-infused vital fluids are required.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/4bbfcf33a8937d3ca47dc7982aac6241.poster.avif?t=1775176158\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/4bbfcf33a8937d3ca47dc7982aac6241.webm?t=1775176158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/4bbfcf33a8937d3ca47dc7982aac6241.mp4?t=1775176158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/9a8220246a71127d2118725595e942f3.poster.avif?t=1775176158\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/9a8220246a71127d2118725595e942f3.webm?t=1775176158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/9a8220246a71127d2118725595e942f3.mp4?t=1775176158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of each stage, powerful final bosses await. Once they are defeated, you will need to put in even &quot;greater effort&quot; to ensure they are fully purified.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/7fcc0cbe27aa49e6e770238c3226ef5b.avif?t=1775176158\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4542410/extras/13b2400fb38c6f66f40823dbb9644f51.avif?t=1775176158\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between stages, you can strengthen Sho us